    "Of the 430 sources included for review, 27 duplicates were identified and removed, and 403 studies were screened for eligibility in two stages.",
    "First, titles and abstracts were screened for further analysis, with the main criteria being that the study analyzes some form of inherent bias (as identified earlier) in a medical context.",
    "This phase excluded 191 articles (Figure 1).",
    "Next, a full-text review was conducted on the remaining 212 articles.",
